{"tid":2005681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【內會爭議】梁君彥引述外聘法律意見 被揭未公開部份內容 民主派轟隱瞞","createTime":"2020-05-07T09:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T09:19:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99c3c6d229da1e1355d7fa6d1f8fa28178c632d5","tid":2005681,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"立法會內務委員會的主席選舉風波，在「大主席」梁君彥委聘外界資深大律師提供法律意見，指內會在任主席李慧琼可以在未選出新任主席前，處理內會事務之後，又再掀起新一輪爭議。立法會秘書處今日承認，外聘的法律意見中，有另一份內容未公開。秘書處指，該法律意見的內容，可能與訴訟程序有關，因此梁君彥認為有需要保留法律專業保密權。有民主派立法會議員則表明，會發信要求梁君彥交代。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%83%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E5%A4%96%E8%81%98%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E6%9C%AA%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E8%BD%9F%E9%9A%B1%E7%9E%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%2581%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%25BD%259F%25E9%259A%25B1%25E7%259E%259E%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=26ef4118\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%2581%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%